<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-TW" class="bg-[#121212] text-[#e0e0e0] antialiased">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Personal Space</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
</head>
<body class="max-w-2xl mx-auto px-6 py-16 md:py-24 tracking-tight">

    <!-- 1. 個人主視覺 / Identity -->
    <header class="mb-14">
        <div class="flex items-center space-x-4 mb-4">
            <!-- 頭像區：這裡預設用一個極簡的文字徽章代替 -->
            <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-zinc-800 flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold text-lg border border-zinc-700">
                P
            </div>
            <div>
                <h1 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white">饗泰多泰式風格餐廳</h1>
                <p class="text-zinc-400 text-sm">Operating Manager / Creator</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <p class="text-zinc-400 leading-relaxed text-sm max-w-lg">
            潮流泰國菜名店，集泰國各區特色料理，名人狂推黃咖哩軟殼蟹、厚切2cm月亮蝦餅與海鮮烘蛋，熱情酸香鮮辣，只為擄獲你的味蕾！來到饗泰多，不用想太多，因為我們都幫你想好了！
        </p>
    </header>

    <!-- 2. 精選項目 / Featured Projects -->
    <main class="mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-[11px] font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-zinc-500 mb-6">精選項目 / Portfolio</h2>
        
        <div class="space-y-3">
            <!-- 項目 1 -->
            <div class="block p-4 rounded-xl border border-zinc-800/80 bg-zinc-900/30 hover:bg-zinc-900/60 hover:border-zinc-700 transition-all duration-200 group">
                <div class="flex justify-between items-start">
                    <div>
                        <h3 class="text-white font-medium group-hover:text-amber-400 transition-colors text-sm">Brand Identity Design</h3>
                        <p class="text-zinc-400 text-xs mt-1">針對連鎖餐飲品牌進行的視覺與 IP 角色重塑企劃。</p>
                    </div>
                    <span class="text-[10px] text-zinc-500 bg-zinc-800/60 px-2 py-0.5 rounded border border-zinc-700/50">2026</span>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <!-- 項目 2 -->
            <div class="block p-4 rounded-xl border border-zinc-800/80 bg-zinc-900/30 hover:bg-zinc-900/60 hover:border-zinc-700 transition-all duration-200 group">
                <div class="flex justify-between items-start">
                    <div>
                        <h3 class="text-white font-medium group-hover:text-amber-400 transition-colors text-sm">Data-Driven Management</h3>
                        <p class="text-zinc-400 text-xs mt-1">整合營運指標與成本分析，打造自動化數據儀表板。</p>
                    </div>
                    <span class="text-[10px] text-zinc-500 bg-zinc-800/60 px-2 py-0.5 rounded border border-zinc-700/50">Analytics</span>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </main>

    <!-- 3. 底部聯絡資訊 / Contact & Links -->
    <footer class="border-t border-zinc-800/60 pt-6 flex justify-between items-center text-[11px] text-zinc-500">
        <div class="flex space-x-4">
            <a href="#" class="hover:text-zinc-300 transition-colors">GitHub</a>
            <a href="#" class="hover:text-zinc-300 transition-colors">Instagram</a>
            <a href="#" class="hover:text-zinc-300 transition-colors">Email</a>
        </div>
        <div class="font-mono text-[10px]">© 2026. Powered by Vercel.</div>
    </footer>

</body>
</html>
